                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n                <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <date>Feb 25th</date>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">It was with deep re-<lb/>gret that I heard through our friend\n                    <persName>Rebecca</persName> that<lb/> you had been sick &amp; that you were\n                still feeble<lb/> although recovered. I ardently hope you may<lb/> be perfectly well\n                ere this <sic>receit</sic> of this. I fear<lb/> you exert your physical strength\n                that it may<lb/> keep pace with the vigor of your mental power<lb/> now that I must\n                ask you not to do for the<lb/> activity of your mind tends to weaken a\n                constitu<lb/>tion not naturally robust. If you would keep<lb/> your mind in repose I\n                am satisfied your<lb/> health would improve I must beg you to be<lb/> more watchful\n                of it &amp; remember you belong<lb/> to your people who cannot afford that you<lb/>\n                exercise your strength to its inquiry. You are too<lb/> important to our spiritual\n                health for us to allow<lb/> you without a caution to neglect yourself.<lb/> My son\n                begs to be kindly remembered I know not<lb/> whether my commendation or your own\n                kind attentions<lb/> have impressed him so favorably but certain it is<lb/> that he\n                awards you all the merit you do readily<lb/> deserve. <persName>S A</persName> has\n                just come home from a long<lb/> visit to <placeName>Johns island</placeName>. She is\n                much improved in health<lb/> &amp; looks from the change; pure country air &amp; the\n                repose</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3hx1670z/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
