                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>which roaming in the woods &amp; communing with nature in<lb/> her unsophisticated\n                state is well calculated to improve<lb/> the health &amp; the heart. The young\n                people have had it quite<lb/> gay this winter there have been several private balls\n                &amp;<lb/> sociables &amp; the arrival of strangers in the winter season<lb/> keeps\n                those who desire society constantly in it. I have<lb/> been in such close mourning\n                for the 2 past years<lb/> that I have been nowhere but where misfortune &amp; ill\n                health<lb/> preside. I however am determined if God protects us from any<lb/> ill I\n                will for my Childrens sake visit &amp; have company at home<lb/> &amp; then I dare\n                say catch a portion of their gaiety Even though<lb/> you were industrious in your\n                efforts that my son should<lb/> captivate some of the fair assembly at the\n                    <add>?</add> Malgré<lb/> toute cela he has returned unscathed not but that\n                I<lb/> should be delighted for him to marry for there only is true<lb/> happiness to\n                be enjoyed <add>?</add> the marriage is of<lb/> two of congenial feelings &amp;\n                habits. The new minister<lb/> is expected in <date>May</date> I do not anticipate so\n                beneficial a<lb/> change as many. I am of a strange turn when content<lb/> with\n                present state of things I prefer no change even<lb/> though it may be a beneficial\n                one I always fear to<lb/> require too much both from Creator &amp; fellow<lb/>\n                Mortals it is more a superstitious fear than an<lb/> amiable trait For I have found\n                that to rest our<lb/> hopes too <add>?</add> on any one desire often ends in<lb/>\n                disappointment And the trials I have had to encounter<lb/> have checked all aspiring\n                desires. I am on the <add>?</add><lb/><add>?</add> to receive my daguerres I presume\n                you know<lb/>\n                <persName>Rebecca</persName> is going to send me her &amp; her dear pets it is</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3hx1670z/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
